{
  "stem": "4187.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So that-- this-- this was my feeling.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My instinct was to get out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My mother, on the other hand, didn't believe that my sister was dead, so she felt that there is-- my sister is there somewhere.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, of course, we didn't know that my father was dead.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So she said, you know, my father is there, so she didn't want to go.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This sounds as if one had a choice.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Of course, one didn't.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But this was a more or less a theoretical thing, that I kept saying we've got to, we've got to.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And she kept saying, I'm not going anywhere.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I'm staying here, because-- because Zsuzsa and-- and my father is there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the way the-- the system worked, when there was a selection, a big selection, they-- they had a cordon, a line, a human cordon made, so that people couldn't hide beyond-- you couldn't go beyond that cordon.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because, obviously, everyone tried to hide, because everyone was frightened of-- of straight into the gas chamber, with good reason.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So my mother, because she had a position, because she was the camp doctor, didn't have to-- didn't have to appear at the selection.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She was exempt.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In fact, I rather think that she wasn't allowed-- I think.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, the cordon was made up by people who had some sort of a job, whether that was-- whatever-- whatever.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "People who were bringing the food in-- that was a job.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Or people who-- oh, I don't know-- whatever.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But they had some sort of standing, and they made up the-- the cordon.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, of course, my sister and I had nothing like that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my mother-- came a selection.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
